  "reference_number": "RUS0707",
  "remarks": "\nBy virtue of his senior position in the State Border Committee of the Republic of Belarus, Vladislav Leonidovich BRUEV has been, and is, involved in engaging or providing support for action which destabilises Ukraine or undermines or threatens the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine, namely, having allowed, and allowing, Russian forces to cross the border as part of the invasion of Ukraine.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
